# PostHog analytics configuration. Copy this file to .env.local and fill in
# your real project token. .env.local is gitignored.
#
# Find your project API key (starts with phc_) in your PostHog project at:
#   Settings → Project → Project API Key
#
# This project uses a reverse proxy: events are sent to /ingest/* which is
# rewritten in next.config.ts to PostHog's hosts. To bypass the proxy (e.g.,
# debugging), set NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST to the direct PostHog host such as
# https://eu.i.posthog.com or https://us.i.posthog.com.

NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_PROJECT_TOKEN=phc_your_project_api_key_here
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST=/ingest
